OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FA woman with an aggressive form of
OL,7,Fbrain cancer has told how she chose to
OL,8,Fsell her house to pay for potentially
OL,9,Flife-extending treatment that is not
OL,10,Favailable on the NHS.
OL,12,FJo Fuller, 51, said it was one of the
OL,13,F"hardest decisions" she had ever made,
OL,14,Fbut was her only hope of accessing
OL,15,Ftreatment that may give her more time.
OL,17,FThe charity Brain Tumour Research is
OL,18,Fnow urging the Government to invest in
OL,19,Fresearch and expand access to clinical
OL,20,Ftrials so "patients are not faced with
OL,21,Fthese difficult and costly decisions".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@SO]|D@KOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FMrs Fuller, a dyslexia specialist from
OL,7,FEast Leake in Nottinghamshire, was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with glioblastoma while on
OL,9,Fholiday in Australia almost two years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FAfter standard treatments did not
OL,13,Fwork, she opted to sell her house to
OL,14,Fcontinue accessing specialist care.
OL,16,FShe has funded hyperthermia treatment,
OL,17,Fwhich heats tumour tissues to between
OL,18,F42C and 43C, alongside regular
OL,19,Fconsultations with an alternative
OL,20,Foncologist, repurposed medication and
OL,21,Fnutritional supplements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FHyperthermia is used alongside
OL,7,Fradiotherapy and chemotherapy to make
OL,8,Fcancer cells more vulnerable to other
OL,9,Ftherapies.
OL,11,FThe treatment is not routinely funded
OL,12,For widely available on the NHS ` it is
OL,13,Fonly used by specialist teams for
OL,14,Fcertain cancers, such as a specific
OL,15,Ftype of bladder cancer.
OL,17,FIts use to treat brain tumours is
OL,18,Flargely experimental, but can be
OL,19,Faccessed through trials or private
OL,20,Fclinics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FMrs Fuller said: "Selling my house was
OL,7,Fone of the hardest decisions I've ever
OL,8,Fmade, but it became my only way of
OL,9,Faccessing treatments that might give
OL,10,Fme more time.
OL,12,F"I never imagined I'd have to sell my
OL,13,Fhome simply to keep fighting for my
OL,14,Flife."
OL,16,FIn December 2024, Mrs Fuller had
OL,17,Ftravelled to Australia with her
OL,18,Fhusband Wayne to spend Christmas with
OL,19,Fhis family.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
