CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FThe couple were planning to move to
OL,7,Fthe country for two years and said it
OL,8,Ffelt like their future was "falling
OL,9,Finto place".
OL,11,FHowever, she collapsed on Boxing Day.
OL,13,F"We'd been shopping for a family
OL,14,Fbarbecue before relaxing outside
OL,15,Foverlooking the sea," she said.
OL,17,F"The next thing I remember was waking
OL,18,Fup on the dining room floor surrounded
OL,19,Fby paramedics. I had no idea I'd
OL,20,Fsuffered a seizure and stopped
OL,21,Fbreathing."
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@KO]uD@AOUwD@UO]yD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FMrs Fuller was diagnosed with
OL,7,Fglioblastoma and had brain surgery in
OL,8,FAustralia.
OL,10,FShe described the experience as
OL,11,F"terrifying".
OL,13,FMrs Fuller returned to the UK three
OL,14,Fand a half months later to have
OL,15,Fradiotherapy and chemotherapy.
OL,17,FThe couple also brought forward their
OL,18,Fplanned handfasting ` a symbolic
OL,19,Fmarriage ritual ` after being told not
OL,20,Fto delay important milestones.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FMrs Fuller's first post-treatment scan
OL,7,Fshowed the tumour had continued to
OL,8,Fgrow aggressively and spread across
OL,9,Fher brain.
OL,11,FShe is no longer having hyperthermia
OL,12,Ftreatment while she is off
OL,13,Fchemotherapy but continues to pay for
OL,14,Fthree-monthly consultations,
OL,15,Frepurposed medication and supplements,
OL,16,Fwhich cost hundreds of pounds each
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,19,FMrs Fuller has also put funds to one
OL,20,Fside in case future scans show her
OL,21,Ftumour has grown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FIn that case, she hopes to pursue IOZK
OL,7,Fimmunotherapy treatment in Germany,
OL,8,Fwhich is not licensed in the UK.
OL,10,FShe said: "I've always told myself
OL,11,FI'll be part of the 1% of long-term
OL,12,Fsurvivors.
OL,14,F"I refuse to let glioblastoma decide
OL,15,Fmy future, but there desperately needs
OL,16,Fto be more research so families like
OL,17,Fmine have better treatment options and
OL,18,Fmore hope."
OL,26,@rD@KOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FAbout 3,200 people each year are
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with glioblastoma, with a
OL,8,Fthird surviving beyond a year.
OL,10,FJust 4% of patients survive behind
OL,11,Ffive years.
OL,13,FDr Karen Noble, director of research,
OL,14,Fpolicy and innovation at Brain Tumour
OL,15,FResearch, said: "Jo's story reflects
OL,16,Fthe devastating reality faced by so
OL,17,Fmany patients and families across the
OL,18,FUK.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,F"With few options, some patients turn
OL,7,Fto treatments abroad, often
OL,8,Funavailable in the UK and without any
OL,9,Fguarantee of better outcomes or
OL,10,Fimproved quality of life, raising
OL,11,Fsubstantial funds to cover these costs.
OL,13,F"We urgently need Government to
OL,14,Fincrease the national investment in
OL,15,Fresearch and expand access to
OL,16,Finnovative trials here in the UK so
OL,17,Fpatients are not faced with these
OL,18,Fdifficult and costly decisions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,FMrs Fuller said: "I may not be able to
OL,7,Fchange my own diagnosis, but I hope
OL,8,Fthat by sharing my story I can help
OL,9,Fraise awareness of glioblastoma and
OL,10,Fthe urgent need for more research.
OL,12,F"No one should have to sell their home
OL,13,Fto access treatments that might
OL,14,Fprolong their life, and no family
OL,15,Fshould feel as though there are no
OL,16,Fmore options simply because research
OL,17,Fhasn't progressed quickly enough.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,F"I hope that one day, people diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith this disease will have far more
OL,8,Fhope than I was given, and that's why
OL,9,FI'll keep telling my story."
OL,11,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "Our deepest
OL,13,Fsympathies are with Jo Fuller, and
OL,14,Feveryone impacted by glioblastoma and
OL,15,Fother brain tumours.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]tD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,F"Improving cancer research and care is
OL,7,Fa priority for this government. That's
OL,8,Fwhy, as part of our National Cancer
OL,9,FPlan, we will bring the latest
OL,10,Fscientific breakthroughs into the NHS
OL,11,Ffaster so that patients can benefit
OL,12,Ffrom earlier diagnosis and more
OL,13,Feffective treatment to live well for
OL,14,Flonger.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784249266
OL,3,CWoman sells house to fund fight
OL,4,Cagainst aggressive brain cancer
OL,6,F"While we know there is more to do,
OL,7,Fthrough the National Institute for
OL,8,FHealth and Care Research (NIHR), we
OL,9,Fare also supporting groundbreaking
OL,10,Ftrials to transform outcomes for
OL,11,Fpeople living with brain tumours, and
OL,12,Ftheir families."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@PO]
